{"tid":2331874,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉股價飆近6％ Elon Musk財富1日大增逾2500億","createTime":"2020-12-19T07:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T10:09:04.000Z","uid":1086,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52aa3f15fdb59ad335459480264c8aa6090963d3","tid":2331874,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95aHro5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95aHro5.png&h=54c2c70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/12/19/phpoIznNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F12%2F19%2FphpoIznNo.jpg&h=7bed1ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國電動車大廠特斯拉（Tesla）即將被納入標普500指數成分股，推升其股價再週五（18日）大漲近6%，馬斯克的個人財富也在同日寫下新高、暴增近90億美元（約新台幣2534億）。<br />\n<br />\n根據彭博億萬富翁指數，隨著特斯拉股價跳漲，馬斯克的淨資產增加近90億美元至1673億美元（約新台幣4.7兆），其今年以來的財富大增1397億美元（約新台幣3.93兆），是全球富豪中財富增幅最高的1位。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，特斯拉股價今年迄今飆漲731%，週五收盤達創紀錄的695美元。特斯拉將於12月21日成為標普500指數成分股，自11月宣佈這項消息以來，特斯拉已經上漲近70%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3385981[url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3385981%5Burl%5D&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=29d345e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3385981%5Burl%5D&h=43409663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3385981[url]</a>"},{"pid":"10e0e8902d819e2bcef634042a24e31b35e67c6d","tid":2331874,"uid":54486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:17:30.000Z","msg":"13 個個農夫山泉垃圾水，勁撚過馬雲同馬化騰"},{"pid":"510c3940f67f224c6d5eb86b5fc0aa5c865716d9","tid":2331874,"uid":227707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"敎主就嚟追過光頭佬<img